SECTION 1 — HERO
================
Role: Establish the product as the desirable hero. This is the strongest
brand impression of the whole page.

Scene:
  - The product (ref #1) placed center-frame as a clear, photorealistic
    hero subject, slightly larger-than-life.
  - Dramatic editorial lighting with a soft halo / glow behind the product.
  - Background: an aspirational environment that matches the category
    ({{ brief.category }}) — think premium spa-like, soft fabrics, glass,
    polished stone, or warm minimal interior, never literal supermarket
    shelves.
  - Empty negative space at the TOP-LEFT region for the headline overlay.
  - Empty negative space at the BOTTOM for the CTA overlay.

Copy overlay zones (DO NOT draw text — just keep these regions visually calm):
  - Top: headline "{{ copy.hero.headline }}"
  - Below top: subhead "{{ copy.hero.subhead }}"
  - Bottom strip: CTA "{{ copy.hero.cta }}"

Mood cue: "{{ copy.hero.headline }} — {{ copy.hero.subhead }}"
